com.teamdev.jxmaps.javafx

Class MapView

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.layout.Region
          • javafx.scene.layout.Pane

              • com.teamdev.jxmaps.javafx.MapView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class MapView
extends javafx.scene.layout.StackPane
    Represents a JavaFX component that displays Google Map viewer instance and provides access to UI-related functionality. This component can be embedded into any Swing container such as JPanel.

      • getImage

        public javafx.scene.image.Image getImage()
        Returns an image of the currently loaded map. The image size will be equal to the size of the MapViewer. This method is not supported in HEAVYWEIGHT mode and returns null.
        Returns:
        an image of the currently loaded map or null in case HEAVYWEIGHT mode.
